
 Compile with:

make

 Compile and Run test suite with:

make check

 Install all important files with:

make install

 Cleanup:

make clean

 Full cleanup, incl. .in -> real convertion etc:

make distclean



...after it's installed you can use it with either pkg-config, just linking with
-lustr or -lustr-debug ... and including ustr.h or ustr-debug.h.

 Or you can use "ustr-import all", and use the headers only.

 See example code etc. at: http://www.and.org/ustr/
